      "role": "user",
      "content": "i cant even look at the news anymore. its all just... it feels like we're just watching a slow motion car crash. what is even the point of trying to build a life or have a career or anything when the planet is literally dying? it feels so stupid to even care about my own future when there might not even be a world left to live in.",
